name: TOYOL ''Caught Red-Handed" Signed Edition
description:
TOYOL "Caught Red-Handed" is a Limited Edition Hand Painted Resin Toy Sculpture.

TOYOL measures 7.5’’ in height and features a 12mm chrome magnet head to body attachment system.

The World Wide “Caught Red-Handed” Signed Edition of 34 units is handmade by me in my home-studio and includes sculpting, carving, casting and are individually hand finished and painted.

Series: TOYOL "Caught Red-Handed"
By: THEY
Year: 2011
Medium: Resin, Acrylic, Mix Media.
Display Style: Standing

Details:
- World Wide Limited Edition Series /34
- Signed and Numbered
- Dimensions: H~7.5" x W~3.5"
- Movable and Detachable Head (Chrome Magnet)

--- READY TO SHIP ---
Each Resin Artwork is individually hand cast, painted and finished by myself. Kindly allow 2-3 working days for your order to be made and securely packaged for shipping to your doorstep.
- Ships with Tracking by International Registered Airmail.
- Ships to other address for Surprise Gifting to your friends and loved ones.

Thank you for looking and buying my art!

+ THEY +

www.they-aos.com
